Statistics. Analysis of the variance of the results obtained after binding to cells that do not express Env versus cells that express Env was  performed after arc sine transformation of the data when percentages  were compared (82). Differences were considered significant at *P < 0.05,    **P < 0.01, and ***P < 0.001.

